Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:03.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a glittering shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:07.64,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:11.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's point is evidence-finding!\NDon't overlook anything important!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.52,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Beika Art Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:48.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Abstract Art of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:02:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nice of my client to give me free passes for solving his case,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but these make no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they're still pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:10.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I agree with you, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that guy up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, sir! Don't touch the art! And smoking is prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Here goes! Catch it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are we playing baseball and not soccer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan! It's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Didn't I see you at the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were drawing sketches?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:17.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? He was drawing these just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you always draw the same pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why... do I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan. Is he hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we call an ambulance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who... Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even remember my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he have amnesia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! The ball hit his arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My head hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My head... my head hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yamada General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he really has amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. His headaches occur\Nas his memory slowly returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he still doesn't know who he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We notified the police,\Nso we'll know soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoops! I forgot to leave his sketchbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that man's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two, check the emergency exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, the patient you brought in just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I take it he didn't leave through the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about his clothes and things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like he changed clothes and took his things with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:20.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did his memory return?!\NBut then why would he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Why aren't we playing soccer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! It's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it! It's all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You okay, Genta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the man from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the ball hit him again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was strangled with string or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, he was strangled to death, probably sometime last evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His pockets are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?! Bugging the inspector again, are ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.\NThese children discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was here last night, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the killer marked him\Nand mugged him when he was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A robbery, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Inspector! The victim's paint supplies are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paint supplies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His canvas and easel are gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So is his paint box!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His bag, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had such items?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must've been stolen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:04.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, right! Nobody'd ever steal that junk, it'd just weigh 'em down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:09.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Besides, one of his shoelaces is in a granny knot,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}which means he didn't tie it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:16.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The ginkgo leaf in his shoe is strange, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:19.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are no ginkgo trees here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:23.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Judging from his location,\Nhe must've been killed somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and tossed over the bridge during the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:30.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And why did he disappear from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:35.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This doesn't seem like any ordinary mugging to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to find out who he is first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Inspector, I think this is actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'll tolerate you getting in my way, but not the Inspector's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go play somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, then, Inspector.\NLet's have a look at the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow! Talk about dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Department Store
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, behind the house is a pylon on the right and a factory on the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we just find that house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not here, either! How about you, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is! It even has a ginkgo tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,Okita House Cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hayase..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car's brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does she want it so clean that there's not a single hair left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same with the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants everything a person might touch wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me it's to erase fingerprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:18.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kimie Hayase (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still dirty. Go through again and—oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! I have some nice cookies! Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her apron's tied with a granny knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:38.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The sofas and tables are different, and there's no TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's completely different from the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Miss. Did you remodel this room recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's all the old stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I threw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that painting new, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It arrived from the art gallery just two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:05.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad. It'll be hard to prove, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, you go, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:24.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo Hayase (47)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks just like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even that characteristic nose is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:27.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? He's wearing glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did he pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks just like a murder victim\Ndiscovered this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was someone else.\NMy husband supposedly died a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Supposedly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disaster disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:54.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Normal Disappearance —\h7 Years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:54.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Disaster Disappearance —\h1 Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person is normally presumed dead after going missing for 7 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but people in natural disasters or shipwrecks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are presumed dead after only one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:11:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, a rich banker by the name of Hayase
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was caught in an avalanche and went missing a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a good memory, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm such a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, there were rumors that he embezzled huge sums of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was just about to be investigated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the authorities figured it was a sham at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The embezzled money couldn't be tracked down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it was assumed he disappeared with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it was eventually called a disaster disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Conan. Have you told Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He had her verify the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:50.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,District Police Station —\hCharnel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:50.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He resembles my husband, but it's not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.71,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Say, does the late Hayase{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10} have any relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A father, or mother, or siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:02.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No. He had no relatives. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:09.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In other words, you're the only one who can verify his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No smoking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:20.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Incidentally, did Mr. Hayase do paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah! We can check the fingerprints on his old things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:30.08,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My husband did indeed paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was painting in the mountains when the avalanche struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I threw out all his things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:39.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.03,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The media and society started to condemn me, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:47.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}for the whole embezzlement thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:50.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wanted to forget my husband quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, all we can do is take her word for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:13:01.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! There's no doubt that the victim is Tatsuo Hayase{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:04.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's gotta be some way to prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! We left something here last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those cookies earlier were so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd love to have more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that what you "left" here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are there any traces left that the victim was here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Some kind of burn mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ginkgo leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:48.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If they're lying here, then they'd come inside if the window was open...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:53.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute! The leaf,\Nthe window, the burn mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:57.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the glasses-less victim,\Nand the painting on the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:03.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Proof that Hayase{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} returned here\Nwith his memory intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure! The victim is unquestionably Tatsuo Hayase{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've finally found proof of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Really, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Inspector Megure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Come immediately, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, what is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me, the great detective Kogoro Mouri, to shed light on the truth behind this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One year ago, Mr. Hayase went into the mountains to paint
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and was caught in an avalanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He luckily survived, but lost his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then walked all over as a wandering artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,unconsciously drawing his house all the while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year passed, and he was judged to have disappeared by disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, his wife inherited his estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you couldn't have him showing up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her inheritance likely included\Nthe missing money he had embezzled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she killed Mr. Hayase when he returned yesterday, memory intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she could keep all the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband died in the mountains a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or do you have proof he was alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right, I don't. That's because you disposed of all of his things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, you removed all possible fingerprints and hairs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even hired a cleaning company to be extra sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you can't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the victim left behind a connection with you:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a ginkgo leaf in his shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no ginkgo trees where he was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's a ginkgo tree next to my house... and all over Tokyo, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One other thing, for some reason, only one of the victim's shoelaces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was in a granny knot... just like your apron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably, when you put his shoes on after killing him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you noticed one was untied!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not wanting to be suspected, you decided to tie it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Claiming I did it because of a granny knot? Hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have no more of these insults!\NI'll take you to court!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NYou have proof, I hope?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then, let me get to the real point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Stand in front of the painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Miss. Was Mr. Hayase a heavy smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you hate cigarettes, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No smoking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hayase, after regaining his memory and leaving the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stood in front of this painting, cigarette in mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, you opened the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Several ginkgo leaves likely fell inside then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One got stuck to his foot while he was inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how do you know he was smoking there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the burn mark on the wooden cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As there was no ashtray in the house, he put it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not going to make me laugh by saying that's your proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, was Mr. Hayase near-sighted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that painting the way he did at the Beika Art Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he got near it and—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! His fingerprints, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fingerprints? Are you saying there are some on that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you said she cleaned the whole place of fingerprints and hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. She even hired a cleaning company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But think about it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No professional would wipe down a bare painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if he had a habit of grabbing paintings, she would've known!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. That habit began after he lost his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he got amnesia, Mr. Hayase wore glasses for his near-sightedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he lost them in the avalanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:20:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he started getting close to paintings because of his poor vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he formed a habit of grabbing them to get a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Mr. Hayase returned here\Nand looked at the painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his wife likely opened the window\Nto air out the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As her back was to him, she probably didn't notice this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she overlooked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss. Can you explain why your husband's fingerprints
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are on a picture you put up two days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Call the examiners! Check for prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did come here. It's all as the detective said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed him. I drugged his coffee and strangled him with a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, why did you dump him in such a conspicuous spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was finally classified as missing and I got his embezzled money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If people learned he was alive, amnesia or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he might've lost all his money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously! I suffered because my husband was an embezzler...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That money was mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get my time, and life, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have plenty of time. Behind bars, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another great nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Dad! You even solved the missing-persons case!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should hire you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did someone go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lousy Shin'ichi'll never come back unless I look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse! He'll ruin my reputation if he comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope he stays missing forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:43.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You know the score, all right!
